node.rich_text: Mane nathi khabar ke mai aaje su karyu pan ajje mai saware ghav chhokha leva gyo ena pachi mai ahiya online form bhariya ane lagyu hatu ke hu aa badhu saari rite kari lais pan je rite mane badhi vastu samj ma avi eej rite mane potana kaam par time apvano achho malva lagyo suu karu mane nathi khabar pan yaaar aa lloko mane ghare nathi gamtu yaar aa vaat mai bear.cat ma pn kareli chhe pan yyaaar su karvu java dyo je vastu jem thai chhe tem thava dyo hu kn hov chu aaa vastu ne rokva valo badhu je rite chale chhe te rite chalva dyo ane goya rakhiye su thase maar su hu jiviss ke nay jivis su hu aa badhi vastu oo ne adpet karva maaate ready chhu
